Description: <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">Overload</font> your musket with gun powder, causing the next shot to deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.MusketAttack_ChargedShot.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_thrust_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage, and an additional <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Ability_Musket_PowerShot.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> to hostile AI targets.<font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">\n\n(Does not stack with Powder Burn.)</font>

When you hit with Power Shot, gain <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">empower</font>, increasing damage by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_PowerShot_Empower.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_PowerShot_Empower.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

Power Shot deals <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Upgrade_Musket_Power_DmgAtFullHealth.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> additional damage to targets with full health.

Power Shot <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">headshots</font> reduce Power Shot's <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">cooldown</font> by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Upgrade_Musket_Power_CDRonHeadshot.CooldownTimer * -100]}%</font>.

<font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">Overload</font> your musket with gun powder, causing the next shot to deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.Musket_Damage_PowderBurn.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_thrust_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage and inflict a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">burn</font> that deals <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_PowderBurn_Burn.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_fire_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage per second for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_PowderBurn_Burn.BaseDuration]}s</font>.<font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">\n\n(Does not stack with Power Shot.)</font>

Standard musket shots deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Upgrade_Musket_Burn_DmgWhileOnFire.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> additional damage if they hit a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">burning</font> target.

If Powder Burn is a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">headshot</font>, the <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">burn</font> duration is extended by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Upgrade_Musket_Burn_ExtendBurnOnHeadshot.TargetStatusEffectDurationMod]}s</font>.
Shots fired before exiting stance increased to <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">5</font>.

If <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">3</font> consecutive shots hit the same target, reduce all other musket <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">cooldowns</font> by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Upgrade_Musket_Shooters_CDROnSameTarget.CooldownTimer * -100]}%</font>.

Landing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">2 headshots</font> within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_HeadshotTracker.BaseDuration]}s</font> of each other reduces the duration of the next <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">reload</font>.

Increase musket damage by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_DMGIfAim2Sec.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> after aiming down sights for more than <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_DMGIfAim2Sec.InActionTime]}s</font>.

If <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_TwoHitStack_Trigger.AddOnStackSize]}</font> or more targets are hit with a single shot, reduce the duration of the next <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">reload</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">({[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_TwoHitStack_Trigger_Cooldown.BaseDuration]}s cooldown)</font>

On a successful <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">headshot</font>, gain <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">empower</font>, increasing damage dealt by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_EmpowerOnHeadshot.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_EmpowerOnHeadshot.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

Headshots <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">weaken</font> targets, decreasing their damage by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_Weaken.DMGStandard * -100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_Weaken.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">({[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_DmgFallOff.ActivationCooldown]}s cooldown)</font>

Basic attack <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">headshots</font> reduce all musket ability <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">cooldowns</font> by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_CDROnHeadshot.CooldownTimer * -100]}%</font>.

Musket shots deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_CritChanceDistance.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> increased base damage to targets <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_CritChanceDistance.DistFromDefender]}m</font> or further away from the player. \n\nAlso deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_CritChanceDistance_Helper.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> increased damage to targets within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Sharpshooter_CritChanceDistance_Helper.DistFromDefender]}m</font>.

Successful hits with a musket grant a stackable <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">2.5%</font> damage increase. This effect ends after more than <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_Damage_EveryADSShot.BaseDuration]}s</font> passes between shots. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_Damage_EveryADSShot.StackMax]} stacks.)</font>

Grants a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Ult_Passive_Musket_ZoomHeadshot.HeadshotDamage * 100]}%</font> damage increase to all <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">headshots</font>. \n\nIf multiple targets are hit when you get a headshot, the next shot within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Ultimate_HeadshotTracker_Duration.BaseDuration]}s</font> inflicts <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">bleed</font> to all targets the shot passes through, dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Ultimate_Headshot_Bleed.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_bleed_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage every second for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Ultimate_Headshot_Bleed.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

Deploy a trap that lasts for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">30s</font>. When triggered, it deals <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.Musket_Trap.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_strike_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage and causes its target to be <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">rooted</font>, immobilizing them for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Trap_Root.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

Traps apply <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">rend</font> to targets that trigger them, increasing damage taken by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Trap_Rend.PhysicalArmor * -100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Trap_Rend.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

Dealing damage to a trapped target <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">heals</font> you for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Upgrade_Musket_TrapLifeSteal.DmgPctToHealth * 100]}%</font> of weapon damage dealt.
Gain an extra trap per cooldown, allowing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">2</font> active traps to be placed in the world.

Throw a short range bomb that <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">sticks</font> to anything it makes contact with.\n\nDetonation will occur <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">3s</font> after impact dealing <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.Musket_StickyBomb_Explosion.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_fire_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage to all targets within a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[SpellDataTable_Musket.Musket_StickyBomb_Explosion.Radius]}m</font> radius.

Sticky Bomb grants the player <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Sticky_StaminaRegen.Stamina]}</font> stamina when it deals damage with an explosion.

Direct hits with the Sticky Bomb cause the target to be <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">slowed</font> by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Sticky_Slow.MoveSpeedMod * -100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Sticky_Slow.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Slow reduces target's movement speed.)</font>

A Powerful shot that deals <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[DamageTable.Musket_Damage_StoppingPower.DmgCoef * 100]}%</font> <img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_thrust_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"></img>weapon damage, <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">staggering</font> the target and <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">knocking back {[DamageTable.Musket_Damage_StoppingPower.ImpactDistanceY]}m</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Can be fired from hip or while aiming down sights.)</font>

Targets hit with Stopping Power are <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">exhausted</font>, reducing their stamina regeneration speed by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_StoppingPower_Exhaust.StaminaRate * -100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_StoppingPower_Exhaust.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

Targets hit with Stopping Power are <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">slowed</font> by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_StoppingPower_Slow.MoveSpeedMod * -100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_StoppingPower_Slow.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Slow reduces target's movement speed.)</font>

Deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Trapper_DMGvsLowHP.BaseDamage *100]}%</font> increased damage to targets below <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Trapper_DMGvsLowHP.TargetHealthPercent]}%</font> health.

Walking/Strafing movement speed increased by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_WalkSpeedWhileNearEnemy.MoveSpeedMod * 100]}%</font> when an enemy is within <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">8m</font> of player.

Increases the <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">stamina damage</font> from standard shots dealt to enemies blocking with shields by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Trapper_StamDMGPenetrate.BlockDamage * 100]}%</font>.\n\nIncreases <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">armor penetration</font> against targets that are not blocking with a shield by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Trapper_StamDMGPenetrate.ArmorPenetration * 100]}%</font>.

Hitting a target with an active <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">debuff</font> grants <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">empower</font>, increasing your damage by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_EmpowerOnDebuffHit.DMGStandard * 100]}%</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_EmpowerOnDebuffHit.BaseDuration]}s</font>.

After a dodge, gain a <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_HasteOnDodge.MovespeedMod * 100]}% haste</font> for <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_HasteOnDodge.BaseDuration]}s</font>. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Haste increases movement speed.)</font>

Dodging <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">reloads</font> the musket. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Can only trigger once every {[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_DodgeReloadSpamPrevention.BaseDuration]}s.)</font>

Attacking a target with an active <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">debuff</font> restores <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[Type_StatusEffectData.Musket_Pass_StaminaOnDebuffHit.Stamina]}</font> stamina.

Deal <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Passive_Musket_Trapper_DMGOnDebuffHit.BaseDamage *100]}%</font> extra damage to targets with an active crowd control status effect. <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282">(Slow, Root, Stun.)</font>

Increase musket damage by <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">{[MusketAbilityTable.Ult_Passive_Musket_StackAbilities.BaseDamage * 100]}%</font> against targets affected by Trapper tree <font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f">debuffs</font>.
